{"tid":320392,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救)在意大利被人偷左特區護照 靠本旅行證有無可能入到俄羅斯","createTime":"2017-07-13T13:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T02:21:24.000Z","uid":108516,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c2b64b0942ade59467c4c19a90a592ee5cfe6c3","tid":320392,"uid":108516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:28:38.000Z","msg":"事發在意大利米蘭比人偷左本特區護照 之後去當地警局整了張報告 然後在中國駐米蘭總領事館整了本旅行證 暫時靠這本旅行證我入到歐洲幾個申根國家 但最後一站我計劃了去俄羅斯 由塔林坐巴士去聖彼得堡 而且買了在莫斯科回程香港的機票 有無人有經驗知要點做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515b6a493b9b954b7e1a94ed31da0e5c82295259","tid":320392,"uid":85819,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:30:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c8e8cf346ace3d091c4f98a38a1a48b05878de3","tid":320392,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:31:18.000Z","msg":"如果攞到簽證可能入到"},{"pid":"ae14c80293f54a4b54d4c5b494e89bdfd7b25312","tid":320392,"uid":85819,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:31:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5876781cb9eb91f57df600662a2fe59879ead76e","tid":320392,"uid":19165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:34:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事發在意大利米蘭比人偷左本特區護照 之後去當地警局整了張報告 然後在中國駐米蘭總領事館整了本旅行證 暫時靠這本旅行證我入到歐洲幾個申根國家 但最後一站我計劃了去俄羅斯 由塔林坐巴士去聖彼得堡 而且買了在莫斯科回程香港的機票 有無人有經驗知要點做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有無試過打返俄羅斯駐香港總領事館問?"},{"pid":"a0a0096f2939419552cc9150973c7b8ebd1325e8","tid":320392,"uid":67737,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:38:17.000Z","msg":"比著係我，會立即終止行程，返香港繼續返工，下次再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a20dec83a861e2518a01d39666a61d74f72bb4","tid":320392,"uid":1789,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d8/TD_PRC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fd%2Fd8%2FTD_PRC.jpg&h=5d244831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d63e683e2f51dcb7498f4c58bcf6783d439f514","tid":320392,"uid":46018,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:33:10.000Z","msg":"點解會比人偷到？<br />\n仲要passport<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41074f2944abd03e6b67c908c1972693dcf7f6d7","tid":320392,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:03:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解會比人偷到？<br />\n仲要passport<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你知唔知passport係黑市有價有市架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7163a4b989d8eb1fc7ed9ad54b119a54fbec3de5","tid":320392,"uid":3383,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:04:36.000Z","msg":"1. 中國旅行證唔係畀你用黎繼續行程，係畀你即時返港。所以你唔可以去其他神根國家。你應該先向你嘅目的地領事館查詢你是否需要重新申請神根簽證，你本嘢入面係吉嘅，出街被人check證就被人拉去差館。<br />\n<br />\n如果你堅持要咁直接過境，咁呢件事就可能發生係你身上。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.liuxue86.com/a/3101828.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.liuxue86.com%2Fa%2F3101828.html&d=P2iMGuw8WYQJZ4ZThAEl49r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=2b1e975b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.liuxue86.com/a/3101828.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 由於你已經唔係揸住特區護照，所以你唔會再享有俄羅斯免簽證待遇，你必須申請俄羅斯簽證。但正如我上述所講，中國旅行證只係用黎畀你即時返港而唔係繼續旅程，所以你亦都唔需要諗申請簽證呢樣嘢，正常都唔會批(當然你唔信邪可以試下，或者有啲驚喜嘅，不過有簽證同入唔入到境又係兩回事)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ask.qyer.com/question/2598071.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fask.qyer.com%2Fquestion%2F2598071.html&d=P2iMGuw8WYQJZ4ZThAEl49r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=1374f262\" target=\"_blank\">http://ask.qyer.com/question/2598071.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ask.qyer.com/question/3315078.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fask.qyer.com%2Fquestion%2F3315078.html&d=P2iMGuw8WYQJZ4ZThAEl49r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=fd0afc03\" target=\"_blank\">http://ask.qyer.com/question/3315078.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ask.qyer.com/question/3332734.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fask.qyer.com%2Fquestion%2F3332734.html&d=P2iMGuw8WYQJZ4ZThAEl49r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=f08e8014\" target=\"_blank\">http://ask.qyer.com/question/3332734.html</a><br />\n<br />\n全部殘體字source，信唔信就你自己揀。"},{"pid":"1c4868ebce3ae5a858f07f98c1a4484d6ae6e1e4","tid":320392,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:10:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事發在意大利米蘭比人偷左本特區護照 之後去當地警局整了張報告 然後在中國駐米蘭總領事館整了本旅行證 暫時靠這本旅行證我入到歐洲幾個申根國家 但最後一站我計劃了去俄羅斯 由塔林坐巴士去聖彼得堡 而且買了在莫斯科回程香港的機票 有無人有經驗知要點做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梗係得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食住花生睇人仆街最開心"},{"pid":"fa684b6678e07b7eb9307cc44aa24f2476d54dc4","tid":320392,"uid":2235,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:11:45.000Z","msg":"假如讀mbbs 就入到"},{"pid":"ca67f28ad983189e213557866de34621f256c182","tid":320392,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:13:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4b9628534dca56cfdb9e499254eba5f2a632703","tid":320392,"uid":127235,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:16:28.000Z","msg":"死死地氣做中國狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b111eff61dbfd99452a85c4adf2f63adcd06eff2","tid":320392,"uid":54065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:17:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1495514/外遊遺失護照應怎辦？%20記住幾招唔使驚\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1495514%2F%E5%A4%96%E9%81%8A%E9%81%BA%E5%A4%B1%E8%AD%B7%E7%85%A7%E6%87%89%E6%80%8E%E8%BE%A6%EF%BC%9F%2520%E8%A8%98%E4%BD%8F%E5%B9%BE%E6%8B%9B%E5%94%94%E4%BD%BF%E9%A9%9A&d=P2iMGuw8WYQJZ4ZThAEl49r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=6067267b\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1495514/外遊遺失護照應怎辦？%20記住幾招唔使驚</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一般在外遺失特區護照的緊急安排<br />\n<br />\n香港入境事務處表示，當事人如向海外中國使領館求助，使領館職員會盡快將當事人資料傳真至香港入境事務處。核實後，會盡快發出一張有當事人照片、姓名、性別、出生日期及地點等的《中華人民共和國旅行證》予當事人。<br />\n<br />\n此臨時證件主要目的是方便當事人盡快回港；如需到別國旅行，需先向該國使領館或航空公司查詢過境、簽證之安排。補領特區護照手續需時，需在回港後再辦理。<br />\n<br />\n求助：<br />\n<br />\n香港入境事務處「協助在外香港居民小組」24小時求助熱線：(852) 1868</span>"},{"pid":"10fdfba022583f2f869c1094c219c427fc104f76","tid":320392,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:19:24.000Z","msg":"返屋企啦"},{"pid":"2b4e963d8e1cc2f01ff482018e2147caa6c30945","tid":320392,"uid":1970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:19:24.000Z","msg":"有冇BNO? 有既過期十年內都可以去申請emergency travel document,24小時內有 可以比你繼續行程<br />\n大陸個本淨係比你返香港嫁咋，邊撚度都去唔倒嫁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b2739c6aff6bb73b1531a7ca2ec7677920bbea","tid":320392,"uid":26071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:30:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇BNO? 有既過期十年內都可以去申請emergency travel document,24小時內有 可以比你繼續行程<br />\n大陸個本淨係比你返香港嫁咋，邊撚度都去唔倒嫁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBNO都無俄羅斯免簽<br />\n基本上樓主都係買過張機票返香港算啦"},{"pid":"aa6f21ed817a7f0d4a7a19805bbedd7e3bd34cff","tid":320392,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:53:59.000Z","msg":"你有冇BNO？<br />\n<br />\n如果有申請過而而家過左期或唔見左，咁可以去英國領事館申請本緊急BNO，即日就可以出到嘅緊急BNO可以拎去俄羅斯大使館做簽證。<br />\n<br />\n如果冇BNO，得本旅行證，咁幫唔到你，呢本野除左中國大陸之外係冇一個地區承認，連香港澳門都唔承認。"},{"pid":"d6a5cb255e552fa6ad8f02ed8a6884249ba7117f","tid":320392,"uid":3383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:02:45.000Z","msg":"如果俄羅斯簽證要有當地居留身份先做得嘅話，咁樓主可以乜都唔使做了，咁樣嘅情況係入唔到俄羅斯。"},{"pid":"aa556293508303476b1c0256aaa3bf7fdb2f7736","tid":320392,"uid":5777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:03:21.000Z","msg":"passport都可以唔見 你翻香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7145e1c4b5cd6857c5cd1a09e83edf11b4585305","tid":320392,"uid":51744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T19:28:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事發在意大利米蘭比人偷左本特區護照 之後去當地警局整了張報告 然後在中國駐米蘭總領事館整了本旅行證 暫時靠這本旅行證我入到歐洲幾個申根國家 但最後一站我計劃了去俄羅斯 由塔林坐巴士去聖彼得堡 而且買了在莫斯科回程香港的機票 有無人有經驗知要點做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n莫講話入俄羅斯，由愛沙尼亞離開神根都有問題。愛沙尼亞出境一定俾人問你點解入境無印，你拎住意大利張報失紙走去愛沙尼亞，之後又唔係直接返香港。我勸你都係最好調頭返意大利，再由意大利返香港。意大利機場嘅地勤起碼見過你張報失紙，見到你機票返香港（轉機與否），最低限度可以幫你將行李直掛香港兼出埋登機證俾你。<br />\n<br />\n不過咁，若你堅持要試由愛沙尼亞出境的話，呢度大把人好樂意等你嘅報告。"},{"pid":"a4dd0f96ef2b5d07f6efbc5ff33af27f02a6d5fb","tid":320392,"uid":76813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T21:08:54.000Z","msg":"出神根區好大膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0297e7d25f75e3e2cff69eb7474325467ea552a6","tid":320392,"uid":39389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T21:12:11.000Z","msg":"唔試下又點知唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56578a3d232da8e932e56faec086435742dbb85","tid":320392,"uid":33242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T21:55:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a82094dd8008fe7bf7ffef93e8b66cfed303920b","tid":320392,"uid":53577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T22:45:22.000Z","msg":"唔使估，我試過，不過係bc, 臨時護照只係出境用，入境係唔受，完。"},{"pid":"3a5e2db241be93c4677987748a8492d113041ce1","tid":320392,"uid":76813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:13:01.000Z","msg":"巴打可唔可以報一報平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7a7d8e3789924caff80adea3622861a3a997ba","tid":320392,"uid":2235,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:20:00.000Z","msg":"可以試下專材入境 你識唔識玩 ow/lol/爐石之類個d 電競game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c3fded00c51a4b3c7f4d9dc80c37594de6329c","tid":320392,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 8年無renew BNO, 想renew要唔要加簽?"},{"pid":"eda84a36da035234f33880508bc366b4f386d7f1","tid":320392,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T18:55:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4423f093b8dbdcc0a2dc598eeb65d1c8a876b9e3","tid":320392,"uid":3383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T01:50:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔使估，我試過，不過係bc, 臨時護照只係出境用，入境係唔受，完。</blockquote><br />\nETD係可以繼續行程，只要同領事館職員提交行程機票車票證明，佢哋會將你嘅入境之後國家嘅日期寫入備註頁，咁你本ETD就可以有效入境寫係備註欄嘅國家，上限係五個，以往BNO post有唔少巴打試過拎黎去台灣同日本，上網亦搵到遠至玻利維亞成功以ETD入境嘅例子。"},{"pid":"c5ec4b1856bc5cae80ed4feea076d22aaaf8dd46","tid":320392,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:27:31.000Z","msg":"好奇一問，成日聽到人偷passport<br />\n其實passport 去左其他人手上係點用多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5885fdc8e592c94663aac4c30cd750bca7f29356","tid":320392,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:31:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好奇一問，成日聽到人偷passport<br />\n其實passport 去左其他人手上係點用多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做假護照。所以真passport有黑市價"},{"pid":"70d8745da604607691f74b7034af818d2b3b4418","tid":320392,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好奇一問，成日聽到人偷passport<br />\n其實passport 去左其他人手上係點用多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n假護照"},{"pid":"334f8e4cb15fdd010aad468c2df2b784a93aadd6","tid":320392,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:41:20.000Z","msg":"回香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cc5422b3e09544e1ee1a44d09b87623ba5faee","tid":320392,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:45:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好奇一問，成日聽到人偷passport<br />\n其實passport 去左其他人手上係點用多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做假護照。所以真passport有黑市價</blockquote><br />\n最近興直接用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff19fe2a33e18ef37e2a6ff58b1bda9cce485a56","tid":320392,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:59:02.000Z","msg":"British emgerency 去神根國都仲ok<br />\n<br />\n特衰轉呢本就返香港啦，我用特衰入moscow都俾關員頁頁check仲要打上office corfirm免visa入境<br />\n<br />\n英國果本有回程機要會幫你加備駐，因為有朋友係南美俾人打劫要經加拿大做transfer,中間要落地，英國領事館收到個flight itenary就會幫你處理好<br />\n<br />\n中國領事館就算鳩數啦，貪平做中國人的代價，返黎有得拎BNO就咪再續特衰"},{"pid":"05fba274cdeb4ed09f0c834bbe08a4d854f35f95","tid":320392,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:10:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔使估，我試過，不過係bc, 臨時護照只係出境用，入境係唔受，完。</blockquote><br />\nOn9仔唔識同領事講臨時護照要加入境國家<br />\n中國本旅行證就真係898啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248eadf685b6b4ad8ad049c3a15e35810f266a85","tid":320392,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T18:40:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔使估，我試過，不過係bc, 臨時護照只係出境用，入境係唔受，完。</blockquote><br />\nOn9仔唔識同領事講臨時護照要加入境國家<br />\n中國本旅行證就真係898啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪咁天真啦，咪講咗etd只係比你出，入境係睇對方接唔接受你張臨時護照，有啲國家得唔表示其他國家都得，你去揾下邊個國家寫明會接收etd入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1bc411254e8e421b2acbc350d38267fe86fedb","tid":320392,"uid":71057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T18:53:00.000Z","msg":"上個月係聖彼得堡搭巴士去塔林 係Narva個關口俾佢問晒成個行程都好唔願意俾我過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw見到有人話俄羅斯好危險,唔好人云亦云啦,重安全過南歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986a9540ea47cb9aa1aca544ecfcde7bf1cca85f","tid":320392,"uid":33242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T13:43:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8b3097782ad091ab7ba8c1ba1936bb3e2ef175f","tid":320392,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:07:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔使估，我試過，不過係bc, 臨時護照只係出境用，入境係唔受，完。</blockquote><br />\nOn9仔唔識同領事講臨時護照要加入境國家<br />\n中國本旅行證就真係898啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪咁天真啦，咪講咗etd只係比你出，入境係睇對方接唔接受你張臨時護照，有啲國家得唔表示其他國家都得，你去揾下邊個國家寫明會接收etd入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果本野係係意大利發,係咪限你只可以意大利出境番香港?</blockquote><br />\n佢唔知etc加入境國家可以拎去申請transit visa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbcde84ead84bc3811e3bcb92fa9d2285b33f77","tid":320392,"uid":43513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:14:45.000Z","msg":"上年用特衰入莫斯科都俾海關驗屍咁驗，仲打左兩次電話唔知問乜搞左大半個鐘先入到境<br />\n你宜家連特衰都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42975ddfe705b91c813b7e70144656e9282f2108","tid":320392,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:38:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔使估，我試過，不過係bc, 臨時護照只係出境用，入境係唔受，完。</blockquote><br />\nOn9仔唔識同領事講臨時護照要加入境國家<br />\n中國本旅行證就真係898啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪咁天真啦，咪講咗etd只係比你出，入境係睇對方接唔接受你張臨時護照，有啲國家得唔表示其他國家都得，你去揾下邊個國家寫明會接收etd入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果本野係係意大利發,係咪限你只可以意大利出境番香港?</blockquote><br />\n佢唔知etc加入境國家可以拎去申請transit visa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好死撑啦，我就當你剩係喺機場transit, 人哋都可以唔比你入，你估你有張19紙大撚晒咩。你話神根國家人哋本身成員國邊境控制鬆散，比你借道過境係唔出奇，但係並不是比你入境旅遊讀書等等。"},{"pid":"e009075da4d9c51d966100f9daa82bd22246a24a","tid":320392,"uid":38376,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:48:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔使估，我試過，不過係bc, 臨時護照只係出境用，入境係唔受，完。</blockquote><br />\nOn9仔唔識同領事講臨時護照要加入境國家<br />\n中國本旅行證就真係898啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪咁天真啦，咪講咗etd只係比你出，入境係睇對方接唔接受你張臨時護照，有啲國家得唔表示其他國家都得，你去揾下邊個國家寫明會接收etd入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果本野係係意大利發,係咪限你只可以意大利出境番香港?</blockquote><br />\n佢唔知etc加入境國家可以拎去申請transit visa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好死撑啦，我就當你剩係喺機場transit, 人哋都可以唔比你入，你估你有張19紙大撚晒咩。你話神根國家人哋本身成員國邊境控制鬆散，比你借道過境係唔出奇，但係並不是比你入境旅遊讀書等等。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇黎你真係對緊急護照嘅認識好少。<br />\n<br />\n睇返英國領事館出嘅緊急護照，接受嘅國家都好幾十個，我唔理你話佢點少過BNO都好啦，點都多過「一個國家都唔受」嘅中國旅行證，甚至真正中國護照都好，免簽國都冇英國緊急護照多。再講，就算d國家唔提供免簽英國緊急護照都好，拎去對方大使館都可以申請簽證，你拎本「中國旅行證」人地當你廢紙，莫講話簽證，連當前國家離境都分分鍾要先補辦入境加簽先。<br />\n<br />\n你咁愛國，你咪渣住本垃圾廁板出國囉，唔好發放流料阻止人地取得應有保障，人地都有知情權咖。"},{"pid":"2acb814a190e1a7aa9f2b652620ad6aca597519c","tid":320392,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T03:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔使估，我試過，不過係bc, 臨時護照只係出境用，入境係唔受，完。</blockquote><br />\nOn9仔唔識同領事講臨時護照要加入境國家<br />\n中國本旅行證就真係898啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪咁天真啦，咪講咗etd只係比你出，入境係睇對方接唔接受你張臨時護照，有啲國家得唔表示其他國家都得，你去揾下邊個國家寫明會接收etd入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果本野係係意大利發,係咪限你只可以意大利出境番香港?</blockquote><br />\n佢唔知etc加入境國家可以拎去申請transit visa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好死撑啦，我就當你剩係喺機場transit, 人哋都可以唔比你入，你估你有張19紙大撚晒咩。你話神根國家人哋本身成員國邊境控制鬆散，比你借道過境係唔出奇，但係並不是比你入境旅遊讀書等等。</blockquote><br />\n<strong>What an emergency travel document lets you do</strong><br />\nYou can use an emergency travel document to travel to your destination through a maximum of 5 countries. You can also normally use it to return to where you are now if you live in the country you&rsquo;re applying from.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/emergency-travel-document\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.g